SIMPLE: mate
RECORDS: 7

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mate
<hw>Ma"te</hw> <pr>(m⟦aum⟧"t⟦asl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Sp.]</ety> <def>The Paraguay tea, being the dried leaf of the
Brazilian holly (<spn>Ilex Paraguensis</spn>). The infusion has a
pleasant odor, with an agreeable bitter taste, and is much used for tea
in South America.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mate</ent>⟦br⟧

